            "settings": {
              "html": "\n<div style=\"background:#08122A;padding:160px 0 80px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.15);\">\n  <div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(196,154,42,0.03) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(196,154,42,0.03) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:60px 60px;pointer-events:none;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto;gap:5rem;align-items:center;position:relative;z-index:1;\">\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:3rem;\"><a href=\"/\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);text-decoration:none;\">Home</a> <span style=\"opacity:.4;\">/</span> <span style=\"color:#C49A2A;\">Investors &amp; Partners</span></div>\n      <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:1.8rem;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:1px;background:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;\">Investor & Partner Relations</span></div>\n      <h1 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,5rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1.04;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 1.5rem;\">A rare window into<br><em style=\"font-style:italic;color:#E2BF68;\">Tier-2 India's</em><br><strong style=\"font-weight:700;\">healthcare future.</strong></h1>\n      <p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);max-width:560px;margin:0 0 2.5rem;\">800 million people. Severely underserved healthcare. A university-backed incubator with grant approvals, clinical infrastructure, and a founding team ready to build. This is the ground floor.</p>\n      <div style=\"display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n        <a href=\"/investor-deck/\" style=\"background:#C49A2A;color:#08122A;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:1px;padding:13px 28px;border-radius:2px;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;\">Download Investor Deck</a>\n        <a href=\"/contact/\" style=\"background:transparent;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);font-weight:500;font-size:13px;padding:12px 24px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);border-radius:2px;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;\">Express Interest</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"min-width:280px;\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;margin-bottom:1.5rem;\">\n        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.2);border-radius:3px;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;font-weight:700;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);\">Grant Approved \u2014 [Body Name]</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.2);border-radius:3px;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;font-weight:700;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);\">LOI Received \u2014 [Partner Institution]</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.2);border-radius:3px;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;font-weight:700;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);\">Hosted by Bareilly International University</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.2);border-radius:3px;\"><span style=\"color:#C49A2A;font-weight:700;\">\u2713</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);\">Startup India Recognised</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"text-align:center;padding:2.5rem;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.2);border-radius:4px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:3rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;\">\u20b9XX Cr</div>\n        <div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);margin-top:6px;\">Grant Pipeline Active</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#F7F3EC;padding:7rem 0;\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;\">\n    <p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">The Opportunity</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:300;color:#08122A;line-height:1.12;margin:0 0 3rem;\">The largest gap in<br><strong style=\"font-weight:700;\">Indian healthcare.</strong></h2>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1.5rem;margin-bottom:5rem;\">\n      <div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;\"><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">$372B</div><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#7A8BA8;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">India Healthcare Market by 2030</div><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Growing at 22% CAGR \u2014 driven largely by Tier-2 and rural demand</p></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;\"><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">800M+</div><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#7A8BA8;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">People in Underserved Markets</div><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Outside India's top-8 cities with limited access to modern medtech solutions</p></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;\"><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\"><5%</div><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#7A8BA8;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">Medtech Startups from Tier-2</div><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Despite this market representing the majority of India's healthcare burden</p></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;\"><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">3\u00d7</div><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#7A8BA8;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">Lower Burn vs Metro Incubators</div><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Bareilly's cost structure gives startups more runway for the same investment</p></div>\n    </div>\n\n    <p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Why Now</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.2rem;font-weight:300;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 2rem;\">Why now is the moment<br>to back Tier-2 medtech.</h2>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:1.5rem;margin-bottom:5rem;\">\n      <div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;display:flex;gap:1.5rem;\"><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.3;flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;\">01</div><div><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.5rem;\">Government tailwinds.</h4><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">PLI for medtech, Ayushman Bharat, National Digital Health Mission \u2014 all driving capital and attention toward underserved healthcare markets.</p></div></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;display:flex;gap:1.5rem;\"><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.3;flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;\">02</div><div><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.5rem;\">University infrastructure, de-risked.</h4><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">BIU's hospital, labs, and faculty are already in place. We're not building from scratch \u2014 we're activating what exists.</p></div></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;display:flex;gap:1.5rem;\"><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.3;flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;\">03</div><div><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.5rem;\">Ayurveda as a global differentiator.</h4><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">The \u20b91.2 lakh crore global herbal and nutraceutical market has no credible scientifically-validated Indian pipeline. BMIIL's Ayush track is built to supply one.</p></div></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;display:flex;gap:1.5rem;\"><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.3;flex-shrink:0;line-height:1;\">04</div><div><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.5rem;\">First-mover in a white space.</h4><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">No comparable medtech incubator exists in Uttar Pradesh, India's most populous state. The addressable market is uncrowded and large.</p></div></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#08122A;padding:7rem 0;\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;\">\n    <p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.1);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Participation Models</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.2rem;font-weight:300;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 2.5rem;\">How you can partner with BMIIL.</h2>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.5rem;margin-bottom:4rem;\">\n      <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:3px 10px;border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Angel & VC Investment</div>\n  <h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Financial Partner</h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">Direct equity participation in BMIIL's fund structure or co-investment rights into individual portfolio startups at pre-negotiated terms.</p>\n  <div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\">\u2192 Preferred co-investment access</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\">\u2192 Quarterly portfolio updates</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\">\u2192 Demo day priority seating</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\">\u2192 Advisory board participation</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\">\u2192 Deal flow from BIU research pipeline</div></div>\n</div>\n      <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:3px 10px;border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Corporate & Hospital Partner</div>\n  <h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Strategic Partner</h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">Gain privileged access to BMIIL's innovation pipeline \u2014 with rights to pilot, license, or acquire technologies developed within the incubator.</p>\n  <div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\">\u2192 First-look licensing rights</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\">\u2192 Dedicated problem statement pipeline</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\">\u2192 Named co-innovation track</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\">\u2192 Joint IP development options</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\">\u2192 Clinical trial facilitation</div></div>\n</div>\n      <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:4px;padding:2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:3px 10px;border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Government & Grant Body</div>\n  <h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Institutional Partner</h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">We actively pursue and facilitate DST, BIRAC, Startup India, and international grant pipelines for our portfolio companies and for BMIIL itself.</p>\n  <div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\">\u2192 Active grant pipeline management</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\">\u2192 BIRAC & DST applications</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\">\u2192 Startup India recognition</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\">\u2192 International research partnerships</div><div style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\">\u2192 Policy engagement & representation</div></div>\n</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n      <h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:300;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 1rem;\">Ready to explore a partnership?</h3>\n      <p style=\"font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);max-width:480px;margin:0 auto 2rem;\">Download our investor deck or reach out directly for a tailored conversation.</p>\n      <div style=\"display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n        <a href=\"/investor-deck/\" style=\"background:#C49A2A;color:#08122A;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:1px;padding:13px 28px;border-radius:2px;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;\">Download Investor Deck</a>\n        <a href=\"/contact/\" style=\"background:transparent;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);font-weight:500;font-size:13px;padding:12px 24px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);border-radius:2px;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;\">Schedule a Conversation</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
